s/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181026/large/1540520304_9f28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540520304_9f28.jpg&h=fe1efcb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fadecee679666ca61cf0a7f6933b798078a1d1a","tid":877943,"uid":11973,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"住公屋即係受緊納稅人資助<br />\n即係你求緊人俾屋你住啦<br />\n限鳩你咪限鳩你囉<br />\n天公地道<br />\n住廉租屋仲想同人講人權講自由呀?<br />\n你老味你而家交緊幾錢租呀?<br />\n咁唔滿意就交返間公屋出嚟<br />\n頂唔撚順就出去租劏房<br />\n再唔係去買私樓都得㗎<br />\n如果你有錢嘅話<br />\n咁咪話鳩之你24小時煮滿漢全席都冇人理你囉"},{"pid":"4419696554611cd5f2a136a061c7100f33489a05","tid":877943,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fadecee679666ca61cf0a7f6933b798078a1d1a","tid":877943,"uid":11973,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"住公屋即係受緊納稅人資助<br />\n即係你求緊人俾屋你住啦<br />\n限鳩你咪限鳩你囉<br />\n天公地道<br />\n住廉租屋仲想同人講人權講自由呀?<br />\n你老味你而家交緊幾錢租呀?<br />\n咁唔滿意就交返間公屋出嚟<br />\n頂唔撚順就出去租劏房<br />\n再唔係去買私樓都得㗎<br />\n如果你有錢嘅話<br />\n咁咪話鳩之你24小時煮滿漢全席都冇人理你囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}